---
/**
 * InternalServices — charcoal section with 2×2 text grid of peer support
 * services that SuperBenefit provides to its projects and cells.
 *
 * Text-only (no cards). Copy is placeholder/lipsum — ready for content
 * team to update. Accent bar follows the MissionStatement pattern.
 */
---

<section id="support" class="internal-services">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="services-label" data-animate="fade-up">Peer Support</span>
    <h2 class="services-heading" data-animate="fade-up">
      Internal services for projects &amp; cells
    </h2>
    <p class="services-lede" data-animate="fade-up">
      SuperBenefit provides shared infrastructure and peer support services
      to its projects and cells &mdash; keeping overhead light, coordination
      clean, and capacity shared across the commons.
    </p>
    <div class="services-accent" aria-hidden="true" data-animate="fade-up"></div>

    <div class="services-grid">
      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 0ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">Legal &amp; incorporation</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Facilisis leo vel frangilla est ullamcorper eget nulla facilisi etiam.
          Vitae suscipit tellus mauris a diam maecenas sed enim ut sem viverra
          aliquet eget sit amet tellus cras adipiscing.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 100ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">Treasury &amp; financial ops</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Amet consectetur adipiscing elit pellentesque habitant morbi. Cursus
          metus aliquam eleifend mi in nulla posuere sollicitudin aliquam
          ultrices sagittis orci a scelerisque purus semper eget.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 200ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">People &amp; community ops</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Purus faucibus ornare suspendisse sed nisi lacus sed. Dignissim cras
          tincidunt lobortis feugiat vivamus at augue eget arcu dictum varius
          duis at consectetur lorem donec massa sapien faucibus.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="service-item" data-animate="fade-up" style="--stagger: 300ms">
        <h3 class="service-item-heading">Governance &amp; coordination</h3>
        <p class="service-item-body">
          Adipiscing diam donec adipiscing tristique risus nec feugiat in
          fermentum posuere urna nec tincidunt praesent semper feugiat nibh
          sed pulvinar proin gravida hendrerit lectus a.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <footer class="services-footer" data-animate="fade-up">
      <a href="/support" class="services-cta">
        See peer support details
        <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14"></path><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"></polyline>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </footer>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .internal-services {
    background: var(--color-charcoal);
    padding-block: var(--space-xl) var(--space-2xl);
    position: relative;
  }

  /* ===== Label ===== */
  .services-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.14em;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    margin-block-end: var(--space-sm);
  }

  /* ===== Heading ===== */
  .services-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-lg);
  }

  /* ===== Lede ===== */
  .services-lede {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.75;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* ===== Accent bar (MissionStatement pattern) ===== */
  .services-accent {
    width: 48px;
    height: 3px;
    background: var(--color-orange);
    border-radius: 2px;
    opacity: 0.5;
    margin-block-end: var(--space-xl);
  }

  /* ===== 2×2 services grid ===== */
  .services-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    align-items: start;
  }

  /* ===== Service item ===== */
  .service-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .service-item-heading {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    line-height: 1.3;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .service-item-body {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-cream);
    opacity: 0.6;
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin: 0;
  }

  /* ===== Stagger animation delay ===== */
  .service-item[data-animate] {
    animation-delay: var(--stagger);
  }

  /* ===== Footer CTA ===== */
  .services-footer {
    margin-block-start: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .services-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 0.5em;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--color-orange);
    text-decoration: none;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    transition: opacity var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .services-cta:hover {
    opacity: 0.7;
  }

  /* ===== Responsive ===== */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .services-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
